  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Uzbekistan: Establishing Commercial Mediation: COVID-19 Response</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">1) To support Uzbek counterparts, namely the Ministry of Justice, the Lawyers&apos; Training Center and the Mediation Center, to build their institutional capacity to regulate, promote and provide mediation. 2) To assist in establishing a cadre of professional business mediators, specifically during and post the COVID-19 pandemic period.</narrative>
  </description>
  <description type="3">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Direct beneficiaries: Ministry of Justice, the Lawyers&apos; Training Center and the Mediation Center.</narrative>
  </description>
  <description type="2">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The project aims to support the Government of Uzbekistan to make mediation, including online mediation, an effective dispute resolution mechanism in the country.</narrative>
  </description>
